<subSubSection id="B6DC9EABFF83FFD9FF36710ED903FAA2" pageId="50" pageNumber="63" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="FE79CD20FF83FFD9FF36710ED903FAA2" blockId="50.[189,794,1065,1313]" pageId="50" pageNumber="63">
<emphasis id="CCB21132FF83FFD9FF36710ED957FBC2" bold="true" box="[189,303,1065,1089]" pageId="50" pageNumber="63">Comment</emphasis>
: An examination of the 
<typeStatus id="217D7382FF83FFD9FDD5710DDAF5FBC1" box="[606,653,1066,1090]" pageId="50" pageNumber="63">type</typeStatus>
material of 
<taxonomicName id="39C6B6A3FF83FFD9FF36716EDADEFBE2" authority="BERNHAUER, 1929" authorityName="Bernhauer" authorityYear="1929" box="[189,678,1097,1121]" class="Insecta" family="Staphylinidae" genus="Orphnebius" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="50" pageNumber="63" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="falagrioides">
<emphasis id="CCB21132FF83FFD9FF36716ED9BEFBE2" box="[189,454,1097,1121]" italics="true" pageId="50" pageNumber="63">Orphnebius falagrioides</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation id="9A57B0D1FF83FFD9FE5E716EDADEFBE2" author="BERNHAUER, M." box="[469,678,1097,1121]" pageId="50" pageNumber="63" pagination="142 - 155" refId="ref77006" refString="BERNHAUER, M. 1929: Zur Kenntnis der Gattungen Astilbus STEPH., Orphnebius MOTSCH. und Deroleptus BERNH. - Zoologischer Anzeiger 82: 142 - 155." type="journal article" year="1929">BERNHAUER, 1929</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
, the 
<typeStatus id="217D7382FF83FFD9FD61716DDB61FBE1" box="[746,793,1098,1122]" pageId="50" pageNumber="63">type</typeStatus>
species of the subgenus 
<taxonomicName id="39C6B6A3FF83FFD9FE7D714EDABAFB02" authorityName="BERNHAUER" authorityYear="1929" box="[502,706,1129,1153]" class="Insecta" family="Staphylinidae" genus="Orphnebius" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="50" pageNumber="63" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="subGenus" subGenus="Megalocephalobius">
<emphasis id="CCB21132FF83FFD9FE7D714EDABAFB02" box="[502,706,1129,1153]" italics="true" pageId="50" pageNumber="63">Megalocephalobius</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
BERNHAUER, 1929, revealed that 
<taxonomicName id="39C6B6A3FF83FFD9FE7171AEDAEEFB22" authorityName="Bernhauer" authorityYear="1929" box="[506,662,1161,1185]" class="Insecta" family="Staphylinidae" genus="Orphnebius" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="50" pageNumber="63" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="falagrioides">
<emphasis id="CCB21132FF83FFD9FE7171AEDAEEFB22" box="[506,662,1161,1185]" italics="true" pageId="50" pageNumber="63">O. falagrioides</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is allied to the species assigned to 
<taxonomicName id="39C6B6A3FF83FFD9FE32718EDA55FB42" authorityName="BERNHAUER" authorityYear="1915" box="[441,557,1193,1217]" class="Insecta" family="Staphylinidae" genus="Deroleptus" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="50" pageNumber="63" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="CCB21132FF83FFD9FE32718EDA55FB42" box="[441,557,1193,1217]" italics="true" pageId="50" pageNumber="63">Deroleptus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
below. For details see the section on 
<taxonomicName id="39C6B6A3FF83FFD9FEE171EEDA7DFB62" authorityName="Bernhauer" authorityYear="1929" box="[362,517,1225,1249]" class="Insecta" family="Staphylinidae" genus="Orphnebius" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="50" pageNumber="63" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="falagrioides">
<emphasis id="CCB21132FF83FFD9FEE171EEDA7DFB62" box="[362,517,1225,1249]" italics="true" pageId="50" pageNumber="63">O. falagrioides</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
. In consequence, 
<taxonomicName id="39C6B6A3FF83FFD9FD5D71EDD936FA82" authorityName="BERNHAUER" authorityYear="1929" class="Insecta" family="Staphylinidae" genus="Orphnebius" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="50" pageNumber="76" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="subGenus" subGenus="Megalocephalobius">
<emphasis id="CCB21132FF83FFD9FD5D71EDD936FA82" italics="true" pageId="50" pageNumber="63">Megalocephalobius</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is placed in synonymy with the senior name 
<taxonomicName id="39C6B6A3FF83FFD9FE8B702ED90CFAA2" authorityName="BERNHAUER" authorityYear="1915" box="[256,372,1289,1313]" class="Insecta" family="Staphylinidae" genus="Deroleptus" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="50" pageNumber="63" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="CCB21132FF83FFD9FE8B702ED90CFAA2" box="[256,372,1289,1313]" italics="true" pageId="50" pageNumber="63">Deroleptus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
